Trapped Inside a Haunted Manor | Ghosts of Darkness | Supernatural Horror Movie Full Movie

Two paranormal investigators are unexpectedly thrown together in the hope of solving a 100-year old mystery.  Locked for three nights in a house with a bloody and unsettling past, the two investigators must put their differences aside and work together.  Used to exposing fakes, they have stumbled onto the real thing and soon discover the myths and stories are nothing compared to what actually resides within the eerie walls of Richmond Manor.
2017.  Stars: Michael Koltes, Paul Flannery, Steve Weston
